{"tid":1534962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新時代消費地圖(前親共 vs 真愛港商店地圖) 新增IG, Twitter LINK","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T17:12:20.000Z","uid":5299,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"157147960c861281c5d407183c35a68d02c056fe","tid":1534962,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"開政事台冇人理,回歸時事台<br />\n<br />\n地圖Link (持續更新中)<br />\n<a href=\"http://rebrand.ly/NeoGuideHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frebrand.ly%2FNeoGuideHK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=e8988bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rebrand.ly/NeoGuideHK</a><br />\n<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/neoguidehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fneoguidehk%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=9cebad85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/neoguidehk/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/neoguidehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fneoguidehk&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=1129c6d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/neoguidehk</a><br />\n<br />\n舊MAP因為懷疑因有人投訴而俾GOGGLE BAN左, 呢個MAP 係BACKUP 撈出黎再更新<br />\n<br />\n新版顏色更新:<br />\n<br />\n五種商家，五種顏色<br />\n紅 (中資)<br />\n黃 (良心)<br />\n藍 (親政府)<br />\n黑 (人血饅頭)<br />\n灰 (立場不確定)<br />\n<br />\n另外亦開發緊self-host 地圖, 唔洗依賴GOOGLE MAP, 地圖獨立, 新MAP 頂住過渡期用<br />\n<br />\n舊PO:<br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OjPrrU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OjPrrU</a><br />\n<br />\n用Google map整緊愛國/愛港商業地圖，求報料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cNEsES\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cNEsES</a><br />\n<br />\n親共 vs 真愛港商店地圖 集中區 (新增報料FORM)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477598</a><br />\n<br />\n新時代消費地圖(前親共 vs 真愛港商店地圖) 復活集中區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518337</a><br />\n<br />\n用電話browser開條link，會打開Google map，往後係您的位置》地圖就會搵到！<br />\n<br />\n之後有曬pins係你個map度！希望每入鋪頭消費前開一開Google map，睇一睇！<br />\n<a href=\"http://rebrand.ly/NeoGuideHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frebrand.ly%2FNeoGuideHK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=e8988bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rebrand.ly/NeoGuideHK</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾料 FORM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/jjzYnd3AYCcVsENm8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FjjzYnd3AYCcVsENm8&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=a8fc3340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/jjzYnd3AYCcVsENm8</a><br />\n<br />\n親共人士旗下業務, 中資企業都得！有証據就會擺上去！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想幫手入野既巴打請聯絡<br />\nhk.shop.record@gmail.com"},{"pid":"6096acee5c58e248b573ea6379433782edafadbf","tid":1534962,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=617